---
title: Pork With Creamy Leek Sauce with Broccoli & Mash
description: When you’re craving a classic meal, but don’t want to be boring, this seared pork will come to the rescue. Pork and potatoes gets a makeover with a rich, leek sauce and buttery mash – plus simple steamed broccoli adds a welcome dose of greens. It just goes to show, classics never go out of style.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/5ba9874b30006c7d6837a422-4438af2f.jpg
